hopobject.body: I came here to work boerne heb pharmacy phone number Alan Pepper is the chief operating officer of Serviced Office group, which provides temporary office space in a market dominated by Regus, which is roughly four times its size. He says: "We won't win a price war with Regus so the key is to differentiate ourselves in terms of the personal service we offer. Customers know that they can speak to me if they need to, and that makes a big difference."
